  "text": "1. Prepare a sample of 100 cubic centimeters of the set system, mix her and maintain 20-30 minutes. 2. In the immobile external cylinder of device 1 (Figure 1 ) inundate 30-40 сm [CITATION_1] of the investigated system. 3. Put an internal cylinder 2 on an axis 3 that is connected with an electric engine.",
